{"ja475:0.1":"Jataka ","ja475:0.2":"Terasakanipata ","ja475:0.3":"Ambavagga ","ja475:0.4":"2. Phandanajataka ","ja475:1.1":"“Kutharihattho puriso, ","ja475:1.2":"vanamogayha titthasi; ","ja475:1.3":"Puttho me samma akkhahi, ","ja475:1.4":"kim darum chetumicchasi”. ","ja475:2.1":"“Isso vanani carasi, ","ja475:2.2":"samani visamani ca; ","ja475:2.3":"Puttho me samma akkhahi, ","ja475:2.4":"kim darum nemiya dalham”. ","ja475:3.1":"“Neva salo na khadiro, ","ja475:3.2":"nassakanno kuto dhavo; ","ja475:3.3":"Rukkho ca phandano nama, ","ja475:3.4":"tam darum nemiya dalham”. ","ja475:4.1":"“Kidisanissa pattani, ","ja475:4.2":"khandho va pana kidiso; ","ja475:4.3":"Puttho me samma akkhahi, ","ja475:4.4":"yatha janemu phandanam”. ","ja475:5.1":"“Yassa sakha palambanti, ","ja475:5.2":"namanti na ca bhanjare; ","ja475:5.3":"So rukkho phandano nama, ","ja475:5.4":"yassa mule aham thito. ","ja475:6.1":"Aranam cakkanabhinam, ","ja475:6.2":"isanemirathassa ca; ","ja475:6.3":"Sabbassa te kammaniyo, ","ja475:6.4":"ayam hessati phandano”. ","ja475:7.1":"“Iti phandanarukkhopi, ","ja475:7.2":"tavade ajjhabhasatha; ","ja475:7.3":"Mayhampi vacanam atthi, ","ja475:7.4":"bharadvaja sunohi me. ","ja475:8.1":"Issassa upakkhandhamha, ","ja475:8.2":"Ukkacca caturangulam; ","ja475:8.3":"Tena nemim pasaresi, ","ja475:8.4":"Evam dalhataram siya. ","ja475:9.1":"Iti phandanarukkhopi, ","ja475:9.2":"veram appesi tavade; ","ja475:9.3":"Jatananca ajatanam, ","ja475:9.4":"issanam dukkhamavahi. ","ja475:10.1":"Iccevam phandano issam, ","ja475:10.2":"isso ca pana phandanam; ","ja475:10.3":"Annamannam vivadena, ","ja475:10.4":"annamannamaghatayum. ","ja475:11.1":"Evameva manussanam, ","ja475:11.2":"vivado yattha jayati; ","ja475:11.3":"Mayuranaccam naccanti, ","ja475:11.4":"yatha te issaphandana. ","ja475:12.1":"Tam vo vadami bhaddam vo, ","ja475:12.2":"yavantettha samagata; ","ja475:12.3":"Sammodatha ma vivadatha, ","ja475:12.4":"ma hotha issaphandana. ","ja475:13.1":"Samaggimeva sikkhetha, ","ja475:13.2":"buddhehetam pasamsitam; ","ja475:13.3":"Samaggirato dhammattho, ","ja475:13.4":"yogakkhema na dhamsati”ti. ","ja475:14.1":"Phandanajatakam dutiyam. "}